close the plo mission 
the diplomatic tugofwar stems from antiterrorist legislation 
signed by president reagan in december the law classifies the 
palestine liberation organization as a terrorist group and bars it 
from operating on us territory 
us attorney general edwin meese iii has tried to use the law 
to close the 14yearold mission with un observer status 
