<TEXT>
bell takes no comfort from the education rhetoric he has heard 
from the presidential candidates including promises from both 
george bush and michael dukakis that they will be the education 
president 
we should be asking the presidential candidates if elected 
what do you plan to do to lead the nation into a truly great 
