the police chief the sheriff and the texas rangers interrupted the 
robbery rehearsal and chased gene paul and his crony out the 
jacksboro highway nearly to springtown 
after wrecking their car the two desperadoes exchanged gunfire 
with officers as they fled on foot along walnut creek both were 
gunned down and died at the scene 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
pat kirkwood claims he was born in the back room of the 2222 
