much that a main deck cargo power drive unit would not work the 
times said 
my quality inspectors can only properly inspect a very small 
proportion of each aircraft craig wrote they should never 
ever come across missing fasteners missing parts cracks 
bodged rivets fasterners fitted the wrong way round yet we find 
instances of some of these on every aircraft 
